tier application with openstack (highlights some exciting new features like LBaaS)</li><li>The folks at Bitergia once again did some great work analyzing the contributions and <a href=\"http://blog.bitergia.com/2013/04/04/companies-contributing-to-openstack-grizzly-analysis/\">blogged about</a> it today.</li></ul><p>If you&#8217;re already a user, don&#8217;t forget to make your voice heard by taking <a href=\"https://www.openstack.org/user-survey\">this user survey</a> and by attending our next <a href=\"http://openstack.org/summit\">OpenStack Summit</a> in Portland April 15th-18th.  <strong>We fight for the users!</strong></p><p><a href=\"http://twitter.com/sparkycollier\">@sparkycollier</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>
