ack Project Meeting: <a href=\"http://eavesdrop.openstack.org/meetings/project/2013/project.2013-03-26-21.01.html\">Summary</a> and <a href=\"http://eavesdrop.openstack.org/meetings/project/2013/project.2013-03-26-21.01.log.html\">full logs</a></li></ul><h2>Got questions?</h2><p><a href=\"https://ask.openstack.org/\">Ask OpenStack</a> is the go-to destination for OpenStack users.</p><p><em>The weekly newsletter is a way for the community to learn about all the various activities occurring on a weekly basis. If you would like to add content to a weekly update or have an idea about this newsletter, please leave a comment.</em></p>" "http://www.openstack.org/blog/2013/03/openstack-community-weekly-newsletter-mar-8-22-2/" (20822 8404) new 7 nil nil ((title nil "OpenStack Community Weekly Newsletter (Mar 8-22)") (link nil "http://www.openstack.org/blog/2013/03/openstack-community-weekly-newsletter-mar-8-22-2/") (comments nil "http://www.openstack.org/blog/2013/03/openstack-community-weekly-newsletter-mar-8-22-2/#comments") (pubDate nil "Fri, 29 Mar 2013 23:16:36 +0000") (dc:creator nil "Stefano Maffulli") (category nil "Communication") (category nil "community") (category nil "Newsletter") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "http://www.openstack.org/blog/?p=4014") (description nil "Highlights of the week Kwapi: an energy efficiency architecture XLcloud HPC project focuses on providing high performance HPC services, while improving energy efficiency. Kwapi makes a smart use of data collected by Ceilometer interfaced with wattmeters in order to introduce power consumption statistics in OpenStack Nova scheduling strategies. Kwapi is stored on StackForge and a [...]") (content:encoded nil "<h2>Highlights of the week</h2><h3><a href=\"http://xlcloud.org/bin/view/Blog/Kwapi+an+energy+efficiency+architecture?language=en\">Kwapi: an energy efficiency architecture</a></h3><p>XLcloud HPC project focuses on providing high performance HPC services, while improving energy efficiency. Kw